P(Heads |\text{ agrees with predecessor}) = \frac{P(Heads \text{ and agrees with predecessor})}{P(\text{agrees with predecessor})} = \frac{p^2}{p^2 + (1-p)^2} = \frac{p^2}{1 - 2p(1-p)} \neq p
